From: Natalia Kovalenko <natasha.k@variscite.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Dec 2025 14:13:25 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] Change UART device permissions and SELinux policy for
 /dev/ttymxc0

---
 imx8m/dart_mx8mp/sepolicy/artmedical.te | 1 +
 imx8m/dart_mx8mp/ueventd.nxp.rc         | 1 +
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 imx8m/dart_mx8mp/sepolicy/artmedical.te

diff --git a/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/sepolicy/artmedical.te b/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/sepolicy/artmedical.te
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..f701895
--- /dev/null
+++ b/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/sepolicy/artmedical.te
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+allow untrusted_app_30 tty_device:chr_file write;
diff --git a/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/ueventd.nxp.rc b/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/ueventd.nxp.rc
index 4dce18e..9db21ae 100644
--- a/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/ueventd.nxp.rc
+++ b/imx8m/dart_mx8mp/ueventd.nxp.rc
@@ -1,6 +1,7 @@
 /dev/block/by-name/presistdata   0600   system      system
 /dev/rfkill                      0660   bluetooth   bluetooth
 /dev/ttymxc2                     0660   bluetooth   root
+/dev/ttymxc0                     0660   root        system
 /dev/cec0                        0666   system      graphics
 /dev/snd/*                       0660   system      audio
 /dev/video*                      0660   system      camera
